'697' => q~This is a simple system that analyzes the log YaBB creates with each click someone makes in your forum. Use this as a rough estimate of the traffic, browser, and operating system of {yabb mbname} visitors. The numbers in parentheses beside each item are the number of occurrences of that item in your log.~,
