'816a' => q~Default character encoding (Choose UTF-8 for new English only forums, otherwise choose ISO-8859-1.)<br /><span class="small"><strong>Note</strong>: This setting only affects the default English language encoding. The add-on Language Packs have their own default character encoding embedded in the Language Packs. This setting <strong>does not</strong> affect the character encoding for the additional Language Packs. However, mixing UTF-8 encoded language packs with ISO-8859-1 encoded language packs can create display issues.</span>~,
